<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[ادَّخَرَ]</span> الشَّيءَ لنَفْسِه: أي دَخَره.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[ل]</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[ادَّخَلَ]</span>: <span class="c4">[الشَّيءُ]</span> <span class="c2">«١»</span>: أي دَخَل.<span class="c5"> قال الله تعالى:</span> أَوْ مُدَّخَلًا <span class="c2">«٢»</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">وأصله:</span> مُدْتَخَل، فقُلِبَتْ التَّاءُ دالًا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
